quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  13,19,"Ana jwaakumanyilila yanti yaitulusyidwe kukwenu kuumila kwa Ambuje ŵenu niyakuona, mpaka alandane ni jwangalola? Chisimu ŵaakwete lundape ni ŵaakukumbuchilaga"
  13,20,"Aŵala ŵaakukwanilisya chilanga cha Allah, ni ŵangawesesya soni chilanga (chakutaŵana ni ŵandu achimijao)"
  13,21,"Ni aŵala ŵaakulumbikanya ichindu yalamwile Allah kuti ilumbikanyisyidwe, ni akuŵa ali nkun’jogopa M’mbuje gwao, ni kuchijogopaga soni chiŵalanjilo chakusakala nnope (cha pa Kiyama)"
  13,22,"Ni aŵala ŵaapilile pakusachilila Ngope ja M’mbuje gwao, ni kwimikaga Swala mwakolosya, ni kutolaga mu ichindu yatwapele mwakusisa ni mwakuonechela, ni kutyosyaga niyambone yakusakala, ŵanganyao niŵaakwete mbesi (jambone) ja Nyumba (ja Akhera)"
  13,23,"Matimbe Gandamo, gatakagajinjile ŵanganyao kwisa soni ŵaŵatesile yaukoto mwa achinangolo ŵao, achiŵammakwao ni ŵanache ŵao, nambo soni Achimalaika taakaajinjilileje ŵanganyao pannango uliose"
  13,24,"(Achasalilaga kuti): “Ntendele uŵe kukwenu, ligongo lya kupilila kwenu.” Kaje kusalala yakuichisya ya Nyumba (ja Akhera)"
  13,25,"Sano aŵala ŵaakugopola chilanga cha Allah panyuma pakuchitaŵa, ni kataga yalamwile Allah kuti ilumbikanyisyidwe, ni kuwatanganyaga pa chilambo, ŵanganyao niŵakwete kupata malweso, soni akwete kupata ŵanganyao Nyumba jakusakala nnope (Jahannama)"
  13,26,"Allah akasansapangulila lisiki jwansachile, ni kunandiya (lisikilyo kwa jwansachile), ni akusengwa nao (achimakafili) umi wa duniya, ni nganiuŵa umi wa duniya pakulandanya ni Akhera ikaŵeje kusengwa kwannonope"
  13,27,"Achimakafili niakutiji: “Nambi uli ngantuluchila jwalakweju chisimosimo kuumila kwa Ambujegwe?” Jilani: “Chisimu Allah akunnechelelaga kusokonechela jwansachile, ni kun’jongolela Kukwakwe jwaujile (kwa Allah pa kutenda toba).”"
  13,28,"Aŵala ŵaakulupilile, soni mitima jao ni jikutulalilaga pakunkolanga Allah. Manyililani yanti; pakunkolanga Allah mitima jikasatulalila"